p: Immature forms of the vectors were collected in bimonthly domiciliary visits from June 2015 to April 2016 (Supplementary Figure S1). The number of houses visited for collection of immature forms was 18 in 2015 and 9 in 2016. They were not the same dwellings over time. These dwellings were indicated to be the location of mosquito foci by local health agents.
